In order to run PyOT you need:
================================

* Python 2.7+

* Twisted 10+

* zope.interface

* MySQLdb 1.2.3 (or pymysql)

* cjson/usjon/simplejson

* pywin32 if you intend to use IOCP (default on windows)

* setuptools / python distribute to compile the cryptomodule


You also need to compile otcrypto:
==================================

python setup.py build # You can also choose install here, but it might conflict on some systems
cp build/*/*.so core

There is a precompiled version inside the WINDOWS folder.


